# ── Copyrighted game data — NEVER commit ──────────────────────────────
**/assets/
**/extracted/
*.xex
*.xexp
# game packages, if ever placed inside the tree
**/000D0000/

# ── Generated by ReXGlue codegen (regenerated from the xex on retest) ──
**/generated/

# ── Build outputs / run artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────
**/out/
**/build/
**/run.log
**/logs/
*.o
*.core
core.*

# ── Incremental-build cache (byte-copies of codegen output — derived from the xex) ──
**/.generated_cache/
# ── Staged built distributables (binaries + libs for local playback) ──
**/dist/
# ── sources.cmake is regenerated by codegen ──
**/generated/sources.cmake
**/*.bak
**/extracted
